  "comment": "STAGGERINGLY BRIGHT!  The XL 120 at over 100,000 peak lumens, nothing comes even close!\nSMOOTH!  Famous Flare dimming curve! Instantaneous RGBW color mixing. Selectable refresh rate up to 28kHz.\nSATURATED COLORS!  Intense, deep reds and blues. Ultra-bright greens. Brilliant camera-friendly whites.\nWEATHER RESISTANT!  Temporary outdoor use in stadiums and large events no problem. Rainproof when oriented vertically or ±15 degrees of vertical\nVERSATILE!  Pixel-map feature with up to 120 RGBW “pixels” for ultimate control\nFLEXIBLE!  Four beam-width versions: 9° lenses, 26° lenses, 36° lenses, or 50° reflectors. Beam width is user-changeable\nin 6-lens groupings. Other beam-width options available by special order.\nSAVINGS!  One Flare XL120 does the job of multiple units of any other fixture. Saves labor, time, space, energy, and money",
